resources.string: Some super cool facts about me:
My older brother and I were born at opposite ends of the US. He was born in Miami, FL and I was born in Burlington, VT.
When I am sleepy, I start singing a lot of songs. They usually come to mind with the last word or phrase I just heard.
I taught myself how to ride a bicycle when I was 4 years old.
